        <h1 class="about-title">About the Explain-o-matic</h1>
        <div class="about-body">
          <div>

            <p>Fitzcairn's Macro Explain-o-matic is a simple tool
            intended to help make macros more accessible for World of
            Warcraft players.</p>

            <p>I got the idea for this site after spending hours on
            the web myself trying to figure out why my macros weren't
            working.  It turned into an interesting side-project that
            I puttered on here and there before gestating as the
            Explain-o-matic.</p>

            <p>Macros are an extraordinarily powerful tool that
            increases player effectiveness.  My hope is that the
            Explain-o-matic will help every World of Warcraft player
            take advantage of what macros offer.</p>

            <p>Oh, and about the name: I picked "Explain-o-matic"
            randomly one day and just ran with it.  It seems to fit
            the WoW theme better than any of the others I could think
            of.</p>

          </div>
